author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week on the show, we take you to the red-carpet premiere of Marvel Studios’ Thunderbolts* as we hear from the film’s cast and crew. We also deliver a behind the scenes peek at Thunderbolts* featuring the film’s Director Jake Schreier, Costume Designer Sanja Hays, and more! And in the comics, hypnosis turns Bucky into a brainwashed assassin. But today we’re joined by Dr. David Spiegel who explains how hypnosis can actually be used as a therapeutic tool. 

00:00 - Welcome back!
01:10 - Cast and crew talk Marvel Studios' Thunderbolts* at the red-carpet premiere!
09:20 - BTS of TB* with Director Jake Schreier, Costume Designer Sanja Hays, and more 
24:35 - Hypnosis as a theraputic tool with Dr. David Spiegel
